<document id="30173622"><sentence text="Effects of verapamil on the pharmacokinetics of puerarin in rats."><entity charOffset="11-20" id="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s1.e0" text="verapamil" /><entity charOffset="48-56" id="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s1.e1" text="puerarin" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s1.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s1.e0" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s1.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s1.e1" /></sentence><sentence text="The oral bioavailability of puerarin is poor which hindered its clinical performance"><entity charOffset="28-36" id="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s2.e0" text="puerarin" /></sentence><sentence text=" This study investigates the effects of verapamil on the pharmacokinetics of puerarin in rats"><entity charOffset="40-49" id="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s3.e0" text="verapamil" /><entity charOffset="77-85" id="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s3.e1" text="puerarin" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s3.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s3.e0" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s3.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s3.e1" /></sentence><sentence text=" The pharmacokinetics of orally administered puerarin (50 mg/kg) with or without verapamil pretreatment (10 mg/kg/day for 7 days) were investigated"><entity charOffset="45-53" id="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s4.e0" text="puerarin" /><entity charOffset="81-90" id="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s4.e1" text="verapamil" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s4.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s4.e0" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s4.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s4.e1" /></sentence><sentence text=" The plasma concentration of puerarin was determined using LC-MS/MS method, and the pharmacokinetics profiles were calculated and compared"><entity charOffset="29-37" id="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s5.e0" text="puerarin" /></sentence><sentence text=" Caco-2 cell transwell model was also used to investigate the effects of verapamil on the transport pf puerarin"><entity charOffset="73-82" id="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s6.e0" text="verapamil" /><entity charOffset="103-111" id="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s6.e1" text="puerarin" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s6.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s6.e0" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s6.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s6.e1" /></sentence><sentence text=" The results showed that when the rats were pretreated with verapamil, the maximum concentration (Cmax) of puerarin increased from 683"><entity charOffset="60-69" id="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s7.e0" text="verapamil" /><entity charOffset="107-115" id="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s7.e1" text="puerarin" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s7.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s7.e0" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s7.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s7.e1" /></sentence><sentence text="7 ± 51" /><sentence text="2 to 933" /><sentence text="5 ± 75" /><sentence text="8 ng/mL (p &lt; 0" /><sentence text="05), and the area under the concentration-time curve from zero to infinity (AUC0-inf) also increased from 3687" /><sentence text="3 ± 444" /><sentence text="6 to 5006" /><sentence text="1 ± 658" /><sentence text="6 μg·h/L (p &lt; 0" /><sentence text="05)" /><sentence text=" The Caco-2 cell transwell experiments indicated that verapamil could decrease the efflux ratio of puerarin from 1"><entity charOffset="99-107" id="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s18.e0" text="puerarin" /></sentence><sentence text="90 to 1" /><sentence text="19 through inhibiting the activity of P-gp" /><sentence text=" In conclusion, these results indicated that verapamil could affect the pharmacokinetics of puerarin, possibly by increasing the systemic exposure of puerarin by inhibiting the activity of P-gp"><entity charOffset="45-54" id="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s21.e0" text="verapamil" /><entity charOffset="92-100" id="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s21.e1" text="puerarin" /><entity charOffset="150-158" id="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s21.e2" text="puerarin" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s21.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.30173622.s21.e0" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-Pub